What you need to know:

Otieno said through his slogan “Dondi Mashinani”, they will continue to build the game at the grassroots through the provision of equipment and expertise where possible. “The number of boxers now attending intermediate [E1] [E2] events have risen to 200 and that is a milestone we would like to upheld post Covid-19. No man can stand alone. I can’t work alone. What is saving us is team work unlike before,” said Otieno.